{
  "video_id": "wuUpIs6dMrY",
  "title": "Why Organ Transplants Are So Expensive In The US",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 2430.0,
      "end_time": 5700.0,
      "text": "Narrator: In 1954, doctors successfully"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 5700.0,
      "end_time": 8960.0,
      "text": "transplanted the first human organ: a kidney"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 8960.0,
      "end_time": 11920.0,
      "text": "taken from a patient's identical twin."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 11920.0,
      "end_time": 15480.0,
      "text": "Today, around 20,000 kidneys are transplanted"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 15480.0,
      "end_time": 19470.0,
      "text": "every year, and based on estimates from one report,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 19470.0,
      "end_time": 22793.0,
      "text": "those transplants cost a total of more than $8 billion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 23740.0,
      "end_time": 25369.0,
      "text": "and that's just for kidneys."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 25370.0,
      "end_time": 29450.0,
      "text": "Factor in the 15,000 other organs transplanted each year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 29450.0,
      "end_time": 32520.0,
      "text": "and you've got yourself a booming business."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 34530.0,
      "end_time": 37330.0,
      "text": "Hospitals are in the business of saving lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 37330.0,
      "end_time": 39920.0,
      "text": "Keyword here being \"business,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 39920.0,
      "end_time": 43720.0,
      "text": "and organ transplants, well, they're a pretty great way"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 43720.0,
      "end_time": 45910.0,
      "text": "to add to your bottom line."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 45910.0,
      "end_time": 48135.0,
      "text": "Katrina A. Bramstedt: Transplant centers are a"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 48135.0,
      "end_time": 51495.0,
      "text": "good revenue center for hospitals. There are some"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 51495.0,
      "end_time": 53830.0,
      "text": "departments in hospitals that don't make a lot of money."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 53830.0,
      "end_time": 55199.0,
      "text": "That's absolutely true."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 55200.0,
      "end_time": 58260.0,
      "text": "I'd be lying if I said, \"Nah.\" It's true,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 58260.0,
      "end_time": 60370.0,
      "text": "and then there's other departments in hospitals"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 60370.0,
      "end_time": 63349.0,
      "text": "including transplant that do tend to, yeah,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 63350.0,
      "end_time": 66200.0,
      "text": "be profitable for hospitals, absolutely."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 66200.0,
      "end_time": 67150.0,
      "text": "Narrator: According to a report"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 67150.0,
      "end_time": 69570.0,
      "text": "published by the consulting firm Milliman,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 69570.0,
      "end_time": 72229.0,
      "text": "the average billed cost for a heart transplant"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 72230.0,
      "end_time": 77100.0,
      "text": "before insurance is an estimated $1.38 million,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 77100.0,
      "end_time": 80560.0,
      "text": "and other organs, well, they're not much cheaper."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 80560.0,
      "end_time": 82950.0,
      "text": "Around half of those costs come from what's called"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 82950.0,
      "end_time": 85320.0,
      "text": "hospital transplant admission."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 85320.0,
      "end_time": 87479.0,
      "text": "That includes room and board in the hospital"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 87480.0,
      "end_time": 89280.0,
      "text": "along with things like nursing care"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 89280.0,
      "end_time": 91700.0,
      "text": "and medication during your stay."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 91700.0,
      "end_time": 94280.0,
      "text": "Now, for a heart transplant, which might require"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 94280.0,
      "end_time": 97600.0,
      "text": "something like two weeks of inpatient care,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 97600.0,
      "end_time": 98870.0,
      "text": "hospital transplant admission adds up"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 98870.0,
      "end_time": 102900.0,
      "text": "to an average of nearly $900,000 a transplant."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 102900.0,
      "end_time": 105600.0,
      "text": "Some doctors say these prices are so high"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 105600.0,
      "end_time": 108570.0,
      "text": "in part because the hospital's trying to make money."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 108570.0,
      "end_time": 112100.0,
      "text": "Dr. Preben Brandenhoff: Here's the dichotomy between"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 112100.0,
      "end_time": 115759.0,
      "text": "hospital interests and our interests as doctors"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 117239.0,
      "end_time": 119230.0,
      "text": "and patient advocates."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 119230.0,
      "end_time": 121120.0,
      "text": "Narrator: That's Dr. Preben Brandenhoff."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 121120.0,
      "end_time": 122620.0,
      "text": "He's a cardiothoracic surgeon"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 122620.0,
      "end_time": 125180.0,
      "text": "who specializes in heart and lung transplants."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 125180.0,
      "end_time": 127200.0,
      "text": "Brandenhoff: The hospital, they just want"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 127200.0,
      "end_time": 129509.0,
      "text": "to make money to run the hospital."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 129508.99999999999,
      "end_time": 132331.0,
      "text": "If you want to be really stone-cold,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 132331.0,
      "end_time": 134640.0,
      "text": "they're not into taking care of patients."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 134640.0,
      "end_time": 136559.0,
      "text": "Narrator: But Dr. Brandenhoff says there's a reason"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 136560.0,
      "end_time": 139600.0,
      "text": "why transplants are so much more expensive"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 139600.0,
      "end_time": 140760.0,
      "text": "than other procedures."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 140760.0,
      "end_time": 143429.0,
      "text": "Take heart bypass surgery for example."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 143430.0,
      "end_time": 146600.0,
      "text": "It can cost up to $130,000,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 146600.0,
      "end_time": 147650.0,
      "text": "but that's just a fraction of the cost"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 147650.0,
      "end_time": 149130.0,
      "text": "of a heart transplant."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 149130.0,
      "end_time": 151560.0,
      "text": "To understand why, just consider what it takes"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 151560.0,
      "end_time": 153720.0,
      "text": "to transplant an organ."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 153720.0,
      "end_time": 155530.0,
      "text": "If the organ donor is deceased,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 155530.0,
      "end_time": 157200.0,
      "text": "there's the expensive medication"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 157200.0,
      "end_time": 158840.0,
      "text": "to keep the organs healthy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 158840.0,
      "end_time": 160750.0,
      "text": "then there's the charted flights"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 160750.0,
      "end_time": 163400.0,
      "text": "to get the organs where they need to go."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 163400.0,
      "end_time": 165310.0,
      "text": "Brandenhoff: If it is one of these"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 165310.0,
      "end_time": 167930.0,
      "text": "where I go to Hawaii and get the lungs"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 167930.0,
      "end_time": 170110.0,
      "text": "because from the time I have the lungs out"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 170110.0,
      "end_time": 172840.0,
      "text": "and ready to go, it'll be five hours going"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 172840.0,
      "end_time": 174330.0,
      "text": "back to the mainland."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 174330.0,
      "end_time": 176555.0,
      "text": "Narrator: And then there's all the trained personnel."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 176555.0,
      "end_time": 178820.0,
      "text": "Bramstedt: So you may have 10 surgeons"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 178820.0,
      "end_time": 182900.0,
      "text": "in an operating room working, so it's huge."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 182900.0,
      "end_time": 184460.0,
      "text": "Narrator: And each of those surgeons is"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 184460.0,
      "end_time": 185973.0,
      "text": "making a lot of money."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 186860.0,
      "end_time": 189470.0,
      "text": "According to Salary.com, the average base salary"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 189470.0,
      "end_time": 191280.0,
      "text": "for a heart transplant surgeon is"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 191280.0,
      "end_time": 195770.0,
      "text": "over $600,000 a year compared to, say, a trauma surgeon"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 195770.0,
      "end_time": 198470.0,
      "text": "who makes under $400,000 a year."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 198470.0,
      "end_time": 201160.0,
      "text": "And finally, there's even more expensive medication"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 201160.0,
      "end_time": 203420.0,
      "text": "to help the body accept the new organ."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 203420.0,
      "end_time": 205559.0,
      "text": "Bramstedt: It can cost somebody a couple thousand dollars"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 205560.0,
      "end_time": 206990.0,
      "text": "a month if they don't have insurance."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 206990.0,
      "end_time": 209330.0,
      "text": "Narrator: So by the time it's all tallied up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 209330.0,
      "end_time": 213210.0,
      "text": "a seven-figure transplant isn't all that surprising,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 213210.0,
      "end_time": 216270.0,
      "text": "even though the organ might come for free."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 216270.0,
      "end_time": 218280.0,
      "text": "And when you consider what you get for it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 218280.0,
      "end_time": 222533.0,
      "text": "you know, life, it might even be a pretty good deal."
    }
  ]
}